com.paydiant.android.core.domain.transactionflow

Class TransactionParameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.paydiant.android.core.domain.transactionflow.TransactionParameters

  • public class TransactionParameters
extends Object
    This class defines the Transaction information, that is provided for the ITransactionFlowManagerFacade.updateTransaction(TransactionParameters), ITransactionFlowManagementService.updateTransaction(TransactionParameters) calls.
    Since:
    3.8.0.1
    Author:
    Paydiant Inc.
    See Also:
    ITransactionFlowManagerFacade.updateTransaction(TransactionParameters), ITransactionFlowManagementService.updateTransaction(TransactionParameters)
